summary: This is another face preset for RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]Helena face preset. She is a Nord Race.[/size]

[color=#ffd966][size=4][b]Requirements:[/b][/size][/color]

[size=3][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]
[/size][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos Renewal[/url]
[/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127/?][size=3]RANs HeadMesh Variants Type C
[/size][/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?][size=3]Better Makeup-High Res Female Lips for SKSE and High Res Female Face Makeup for SKSE
[/size][/url][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url][/size]
[size=3]
If you want her to look like she does in the image I use [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?][size=3]CBBE[/size][/url][size=3] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54362/?]Somber Dreams ENB[/url].

[/size][size=4][b][color=#ffd966]Install:[/color]

[/b][/size][size=3]You can install with NMM.

Manually download it, unzip it and place it into your Skyrim/Data/SKSE/P[b]lugins/[/b][b]CharGen/Presets
[/b]
In game, pull up the console command and type showracemenu and hit enter, pick Nord race, hit the the preset tab and load the presets by using F9 and pick Helena.
[/size][size=3]
[/size]
